    metaDescription:
      'How to safely buy exotic fish online. Shipping, acclimation, red flags, legal compliance, and choosing reputable dealers. Expert guidance.',
    quickAnswerQuestion: 'Is it safe to buy exotic fish online?',
    quickAnswer:
      'Yes, buying exotic fish online is safe when you purchase from reputable dealers who offer live-arrival guarantees, overnight shipping in insulated containers with oxygen packs, and transparent health and provenance documentation. Key steps include verifying the dealer\'s quarantine protocols, confirming legal compliance for your state, and having a cycled quarantine tank ready before the fish arrives.',
