    heroImage: '/images/blog/stingray-freshwater-vs-saltwater.jpg',
    heroImageAlt:
      'A Potamotrygon motoro freshwater stingray and a Blue-spotted saltwater stingray displayed side by side',
    metaTitle: 'Freshwater vs Saltwater Stingray: Expert Comparison | The Fish Collection',
    metaDescription:
      'Freshwater vs Saltwater Stingray — detailed comparison of care, size, cost, venom, and legality. Expert guide to keeping stingrays in home aquariums.',
    quickAnswerQuestion: 'Can you keep stingrays in a home aquarium?',
