    heroImage: '/images/blog/koi-vs-arowana.jpg',
    heroImageAlt:
      'A Grand Champion Kohaku Koi and a Super Red Asian Arowana displayed side by side',
    metaTitle: 'Koi vs Arowana: The Ultimate Prestige Fish Comparison | The Fish Collection',
    metaDescription:
      'Koi vs Arowana — expert comparison of cost, prestige, care, lifespan, and collector culture. The two most valuable ornamental fish in the world, head to head.',
    quickAnswerQuestion: 'Which is more valuable — Koi or Arowana?',
